NAME

  twit-view - simple twitter viewer

SYNOPSYS

  twit-view [<options>] <query>

DESCRIPTION

  The options are as follows:

OPTIONS

  <query>
    get the twitter of the about the query.

  -s <word>
    word for the emphasis.

  -S <word>
    word for the emphasis.

  -h -? --help
    display command line help message.

EXAMPLES

  twit-view.pl -s japan -S like -S love '#prayforjapan -rt'

HISTORY

  v.0.1
    * '-s,-S' emphasis
    * added searching twitter about the query.

